name: MMSS (Ordinals)
description: $MMSS, initiated by Korean artist SHHAN, is a BRC-20 token with the Black Cat IP at its core. The community's future development includes establishing the MMSS Art Club, MMSS Fashion Club, MMSS BTC Research Institute, and MMSS Education Academy, all centered around the $MMSS ecosystem. MMSS community's goal is to gather young cat enthusiasts worldwide, allowing them to express themselves through a playful approach.
